In the MATTER OF the ESTATE OF Jill A. JORDAN, Deceased. Estate of Jill A. Jordan, Petitioner-Appellant,
v.
Iowa Medicaid Enterprise Estate Recovery Program, Respondent-Appellee. No. 18-0590 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

An estate appeals from the district court's order granting summary judgment in favor of the Iowa Department of Human Services on the estate's petition for declaratory judgment regarding the payment of an annuity. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
